OL,3,CTrail hunting to be banned in England
OL,4,Cand Wales
OL,6,FTrail hunting is set to be banned in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales amid fears the
OL,8,Factivity has been used to cover up
OL,9,Fillegal fox hunting.
OL,11,FTrail hunting mimics a traditional
OL,12,Fhunt, with dogs following an animal
OL,13,Fscent which has been laid and hunters
OL,14,Ftrailing the pack on horseback.
OL,16,FThe Hunting Act introduced in 2004
OL,17,Fmade it illegal for packs of dogs to
OL,18,Fhunt wild mammals including foxes.
