OL,3,CTrail hunting to be banned in England
OL,4,Cand Wales
OL,6,F"We are working out the best approach
OL,7,Fto take the ban forward and will run a
OL,8,Fconsultation to seek views."
OL,10,FTrail hunting has grown in popularity
OL,11,Fin recent years and is also believed
OL,12,Fto put other wild animals at risk of
OL,13,Fbeing attacked by hounds, as the pack
OL,14,Fcan accidentally follow other scents.
OL,16,FIt is already banned in Scotland.
OL,18,FThe ban forms part of the upcoming
OL,19,Fanimal welfare strategy which is due
OL,20,Fto be published on Monday.
